 hy Meyer
DTSTART:20260809T080000
DTEND:20260809T100000
UID:6279c85a4bf772e1026118008cdbd8f5@sycamorelandtrust.org
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a guided birding hike through the diverse habitats
  of Beanblossom Bottoms Nature Preserve. Listen for songbirds\, watch for 
 soaring raptors\, and catch glimpses of wetland species along the boardwal
 k. All experience levels are welcome. Binoculars are available. Cathy is a
  retired naturalist from Monroe County Parks and Recreation and a member o
 f the Indiana Audubon Society and Sassafras Audubon Society. She led bird 
 hikes for the Indiana Dunes Birding Festival\, Sycamore Land Trust\, and o
 ther groups. This event was rescheduled from June 14 due to spring floodin
 g. If this hike is full\, sign up for the wait list.
