DESCRIPTION:Join Education Director Saige Sentell to discover the diverse 
 mix of habitats Powell Preserve provides: forested hills\, bottomland wood
 s\, and a prairie planting with native wildflowers and grasses. We’ll me
 ander the trail identifying native grasses and forbs\, studying plant part
 s and their ecological role. Powell Preserve is not open to the public.
