UID:95746d3479cf37c467339ccf34a162ad@sycamorelandtrust.org
DESCRIPTION:Sycamore Land Trust is delighted to announce our Spring Native
  Plant Sale!  Proceeds from the sale will be used to support our Native P
 lant Nursery where we grow native plants for our many land restoration pro
 jects in South Central Indiana. We will offer native plants that thrive in
  a garden setting and that provide vital habitat and food for our pollinat
 ors\, birds and small mammals. Please stop by and chat with us about addin
 g more native plants to your backyard in support of wildlife.
